title: Consumer spending in Pakistan 2013 - 2018 , per capita
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing U.S. dollars, containing a total of 6 data points.
Overall U.S. dollars has increased over the Year.
U.S. dollars is slightly increasing from 2013 to 2018.

The highest U.S. dollars, of value 1658.0 was reached at Year 2018
The lowest U.S. dollars, of value 995.0 was reported at Year 2013
